13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 255.10 of Title 62, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. The Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall
18 develop a form for use by each agency, board, commission, department
19 or other entity organized within the executive branch of state
20 government for use by such governmental entity in identifying
21 prospective vendors for contracts to manage federal funds if such
22 funds management is permissible pursuant to the federal law enabling
23 and transferring such funds for expenditure by the state
24 governmental entity. Each such governmental entity shall complete
